             <Reference>CVE-2021-32638</Reference>
             <Description>Code analysis product passes access tokens as a command-line parameter or through an environment variable, making them visible to other processes via the ps command.</Description>
             <Link>https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2021-32638</Link>
           </Observed_Example>
